lf' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/5549353397427757807/comments/default/3929540739133683647'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/05/weekly-share-2.html?showComment=1336651648563#c3929540739133683647' title=''/><author><name>记忆め碎片</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/04020567892961640261</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/b16-rounded.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/05/weekly-share-2.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-5549353397427757807' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/5549353397427757807' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1558254483"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2012年5月10日 下午8:07:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3351847749108073310</id><published>2012-05-10T16:22:24.913+08:00</published><updated>2012-05-10T16:22:24.913+08:00</updated><title type='text'>你好，SkyDrive上的f_r_e_e_g_a_t_e请及时更新，谢谢！</title><content type='html'>你好，SkyDrive上的f_r_e_e_g_a_t_e请及时更新，谢谢！</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/5549353397427757807/comments/default/3351847749108073310'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/5549353397427757807/comments/default/3351847749108073310'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/05/weekly-share-2.html?showComment=1336638144913#c3351847749108073310' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/05/weekly-share-2.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-5549353397427757807' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/5549353397427757807' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1162149379"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2012年5月10日 下午4:22:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-7875810877597749005</id><published>2012-05-08T23:15:52.593+08:00</published><updated>2012-05-08T23:15:52.593+08:00</updated><title type='text'>TO Antimony&#xa;你说的情况应该是普遍现象。&#xa;不光中学如此，貌似俺当年读大学的时候，也是如此。...</title><content type='html'>TO Antimony&lt;br /&gt;你说的情况应该是普遍现象。&lt;br /&gt;不光中学如此，貌似俺当年读大学的时候，也是如此。&lt;br /&gt;如今的天朝，风气不好。其中一个原因是信仰危机。&lt;br /&gt;当年老毛通过文化大革命，把非共产主义的其它文化都彻底清除掉。但如今，所谓的“共产主义理想”早就破灭了。所以就出现信仰的真空。&lt;br /&gt;在这种环境下，很多人就会选择拜金主义和享乐主义。</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/5549353397427757807/comments/default/7875810877597749005'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/5549353397427757807/comments/default/7875810877597749005'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/05/weekly-share-2.html?showComment=1336490152593#c7875810877597749005' title=''/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AmZd_cbsMA8/Th5EbQ2_22I/AAAAAAAAAfg/loksvIqGzic/s220/Thinker.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/05/weekly-share-2.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-5549353397427757807' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/5549353397427757807' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1582521586"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="2012年5月8日 下午11:15:00"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-7706170728041866904</id><published>2012-05-08T23:07:40.297+08:00</published><updated>2012-05-08T23:07:40.297+08:00</updated><title type='text'>TO 前6楼的网友&#xa;其实“广电总局”不是关键，关键是真理部。&#xa;广电总局的各种审查，背后都是真理部在操...</title><content type='html'>TO 前6楼的网友&lt;br /&gt;其实“广电总局”不是关键，关键是真理部。&lt;br /&gt;广电总局的各种审查，背后都是真理部在操控。&lt;br /&gt;整个天朝的洗脑和愚民教育，都是真理部负责滴。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;TO 茉莉花s&lt;br /&gt;多谢分享大饥荒的资源 :)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;TO 前3楼的网友&lt;br /&gt;天朝的政府部门（不论是公检法还是信访办），根本就无处伸冤。所以陈光诚才会去美国大使馆。&lt;br /&gt;至于陈光诚去美国留学，据说是一个权宜之计。&lt;br /&gt;陈光诚希望能留在中国搞维权，不想移民美国。&lt;br /&gt;但目前他的处境比较危险。&lt;br /&gt;暂时去美国留学，既保留他的天朝民众身份，又可以暂时避开山东官员的迫害。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;TO 楼上的网友&lt;br /&gt;对于俺博客的五毛留言，俺早就习以为常了 :)</content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/5549353397427757807/comments/default/7706170728041866904'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/5549353397427757807/comments/default/7706170728041866904'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/05/weekly-share-2.html?showComment=1336489660297#c7706170728041866904' title=''/><author><name>编程随想</name><uri>http://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='26' height='32' src='http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-AmZd_cbsMA8/Th5EbQ2_22I/AAAAAAAAAfg/loksvIqGzic/s220/Thinker.jpg'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://program-think.blogspot.com/2012/0